  "script": [
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_sun-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_03-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "サニーピースです！\nリハーサル、よろしくお願いします！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We're Sunny Peace!\nThank you for the rehearsal!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 5.4333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（いよいよ今日がI-UNITYファイナル）\n（サニピのコンディションはバッチリだ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Today is finally the I-UNITY finals.)\n(Sunny Peace is in perfect condition.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 10.8666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（けど、やっぱり落ち着かないな）\n（今日のファイナル、無事に終えられるだろうか……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(But I still can't calm down.)\n(Will today's finals end without any problems…?)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.3433333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-call-02.m4a",
          "delay": 4323.333333399999,
          "startTime": 18.6666666667
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 5556.666666699998,
          "startTime": 19.9
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――二日前",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Two days ago.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 19.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_serious-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 19.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_03-stm001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、三枝さんからお電話です！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Manager-san‚ there's a call from Saegusa-san!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shinji",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "もしもし、{user}か？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hello‚ {user}?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shinji",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "直接事務所に行けなくてすまないな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sorry I can't go to the office directly.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shinji",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "姫野の件だが、不正の証拠を掴むまであと少しだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "About Himeno‚ we're almost there in getting evidence of her wrongdoings.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shinji",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ファイナルまでには間に合わせたかったが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I wanted to make it in time for the finals‚ but…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "そうですか……\nこちらは今のところ、何も変わりはありません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see…\nThere's been no change on our end.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shinji",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "だが、やつのことだ。こないだのゴシップ記事のように",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But knowing her‚ she might try something‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shinji",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "何かしら仕掛けてくる可能性はある",
      "translations": {
        "en": "like with that gossip article the other day.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shinji",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "何が起こるか予想も出来ない……常に警戒を怠るな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I can't predict what will happen… Don't let your guard down.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "もちろんです\nさくら達は俺が、しっかり守ってみせます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course.\nI'll make sure to protect Sakura and the others.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shinji",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ああ……それと当日は、会場の様子にも",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah… And on the day of the finals‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shinji",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "気を配っておくんだ。全てが終わるまで油断は出来ない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "keep an eye on the situation at the venue. We can't be careless until it's all over.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_03-stm002.m4a",
      "text": "気を配るって……あんな広い会場なんですよ？\n{user}さんもリハに付き添わないと……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Keep an eye on it… That's a huge venue!\nAnd Manager-san has to attend the rehearsals too…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.4666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3566.6666666000137,
          "startTime": 80.0333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_03-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "人手が必要なら、ここにいますよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you need help‚ I'm here.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "――え？\n琴乃……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Huh?\nKotono…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage03",
      "startTime": 87.3666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage03",
      "startTime": 87.3666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_trouble-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 91.8961578369
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_03-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、お疲れ様です\nリハの様子はどうですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good work‚ Manager-san.\nHow's the rehearsal going?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "こっちは何も問題ないよ、順調だ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There's no problem on this end‚ everything's going smoothly.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage03",
      "startTime": 97.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_03-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "良かった……こっちも、特に異常はなさそうです\nメイク道具とか衣装とか、必要な物は揃ってました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's good… There don't seem to be any problems here either.\nMakeup tools‚ costumes‚ everything we need is ready.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "そうか\n三枝さんの考え過ぎだといいんだけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see.\nI hope Saegusa-san is just overthinking things…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage03",
      "startTime": 111.9666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_03-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "でも、いつものねつ造記事で追い込むようなやり方も\n今日に限ってはしてきませんでしたからね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But even with her usual method of cornering us with fabricated articles‚\nshe hasn't done anything today.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage03",
      "startTime": 119.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_03-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "目に見えない形で、何か仕掛けているかもしれません\nもうしばらく、会場を見回ってみます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She might be planning something behind the scenes.\nI'll look around the venue for a while longer.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとう。……そして、ごめん\nアイドルのみんなに、こんな役目をお願いしちゃって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thanks. …And I'm sorry.\nFor asking the idols to do this kind of job.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_moon-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 135.1
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage03",
      "startTime": 135.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_03-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "気にしないの！　{user}さんは\nリハ見てあげてないとでしょ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don't worry about it! Manager-san‚ you\nhave to watch the rehearsals‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage03",
      "startTime": 140.8333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_03-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "そうですわ。こういう時だからこそ\n誰よりもサニピの側にいて、支えてあげるべきですわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's right. At times like this‚\nyou should be by Sunny Peace's side more than anyone else and support them.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 144.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣、すず……そうだな、その通りだ\nサニピが安心して、本番を迎えられるよう力を尽くすよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mei‚ Suzu… You're right.\nI'll do my best so Sunny Peace can go into the performance with peace of mind.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 155.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage03",
      "startTime": 159.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
